node.title: Warriors fall to Roosters in Sydney clash
node.description: Despite a promising first-half effort, the Warriors have been beaten 22-14 by the clinical Roosters at the Sydney Cricket Ground.
node.content:
["Despite a promising first-half effort, the Warriors have been beaten 22-14 by the clinical Roosters at the Sydney Cricket Ground.", "", "
Dallin Watene-Zelezniak and Jesse Arthars tackle Daniel Tupou during the Sydney Roosters match against the Vodafone Warriors in Sydney. Photo: David Neilson / www.photosport.nz
", "The Warriors were leading 8-6 at halftime, in the round six NRL clash.", "The Auckland side sits ninth on the ladder, heading into their ANZAC Day clash with the Storm."]
